===Pollution===
According to the World Bank's survey in 2004, Lucknow ranks 7th in the world regarding air pollution, three other Indian cities precede it, they are [[Delhi]] at second position, [[Kolkata]] at third position and [[Kanpur]] at sixth position.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://siteresources.worldbank.org/DATASTATISTICS/Resources/table3_13.pdf |title=World Bank Statistics |format=PDF |accessdate=29 August 2010}}</ref>

==Demographics==
